Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.09,0:00:37.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卻穿著高中的制服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.56,0:00:42.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.95,0:00:55.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夢…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.32,0:00:59.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼…到現在還…
